first attempt at a python webapp
using: python, flask, git
remeber to setup environment variables for flask
    in windows: open up terminal window in vscode (control + shift + `)
                set FLASK_APP=hello
                set FLASK_ENV=development

                if using powershell, 
                    $env:FLASK_APP="hello"
                    $env:FLASK_ENV="development"

                run flask!:
                    flask run 
                        sometimes env can not find flask.exe
                        set it up or go to C:\Users\Hanna\AppData\Local\Packages\PythonSoftwareFoundation.Python.3.11_qbz5n2kfra8p0\LocalCache\local-packages\Python311\Scripts\flask.exe run

    you can also reset/initialise your database with examples by running the init_db.py script
        change directory to cd flask_blog       
          run python init_db.py
         


Changing over the database to connect to the mariadb database on the fileserver at home
